sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant UserController
    participant DB as SQLite DB

    User->>Browser: Visit site (unauthenticated)
    Browser->>Browser: Redirect to /accounts/login/

    User->>Browser: Click "Login with Google"
    Browser->>Browser: Google OAuth flow (django-allauth)
    Browser->>DB: Django User created/retrieved

    Browser->>UserController: GET /user/onboarding/
    UserController->>DB: Check UserProfile exists?

    alt Profile already exists
        UserController-->>Browser: Redirect to /generation/ or /browse/
    else No profile yet
        UserController-->>Browser: Render onboarding.html (choose role)

        User->>Browser: Select role (Creator or Listener)
        Browser->>UserController: POST /user/onboarding/ { role }

        alt role = CREATOR
            UserController->>DB: Create UserProfile (role=CREATOR)
            UserController->>DB: Create Creator record
            UserController-->>Browser: Redirect to /generation/
        else role = LISTENER
            UserController->>DB: Create UserProfile (role=LISTENER)
            UserController->>DB: Create Listener record
            UserController-->>Browser: Redirect to /browse/
        end
    end
